			PPR - MLA Flight#: 5J 636 <br />11 Feb 2015, Wed, (12:00PM - 01:20PM) PPR International Airport<br /><br />
			
			<b>Soon to Book</b><br />
			Hotel Accomodation : FOUR SEASONS 3D2N and/or 1N PPR Hotel<br />
			Tours : A, B, C or D<br />
			Travel Agency : Travelonline.ph
	  </div>
	</div>
	

	<h3>Total : <b> PHP <%= sum_a + sum_b + sum_c + sum_d + sum_e %>.00</b> </h3>
	
  </div>

</div>

